        </div>

    </section>



    <main style="background-color: rgb(72, 196, 214); color: white;" id="bottom">

        <div class="container" id="des" style="padding: 70px 50px;">
            <br>
            <div class="about text-center">
                <h3>GroupMatesFinder System</h3>
                <p>Aims to replace the peer evaluation form, make group formation process become easier and help
                    students to find group
                    mates with good quality. The GroupMatesFinder will keep track of students’ group project performance
                    continuously
                    throughout their university life. Performance puts a great emphasis on the comment and score given
                    by their group mate.
                </p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="features text-center">
                <div class="row my-4">
                    <div class="feature col-sm">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" fill="currentColor"
                                class="bi bi-clock" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path
                                    d="M8 3.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0V9a.5.5 0 0 0 .252.434l3.5 2a.5.5 0 0 0 .496-.868L8 8.71V3.5z" />
