                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4>View past performance</h4>
                        <p>Student under the same course can access each other profile</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm feature">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" fill="currentColor"
                                class="bi bi-lightning" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path
                                    d="M11.251.068a.5.5 0 0 1 .227.58L9.677 6.5H13a.5.5 0 0 1 .364.843l-8 8.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.842-.49L6.323 9.5H3a.5.5 0 0 1-.364-.843l8-8.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .615-.09zM4.157 8.5H7a.5.5 0 0 1 .478.647L6.11 13.59l5.732-6.09H9a.5.5 0 0 1-.478-.647L9.89 2.41 4.157 8.5z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Form group</h4>
                        <p>Create a group or apply to join a group.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm feature">
                        <div class="mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80"
                                fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-clipboard-data" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path
                                    d="M4 11a1 1 0 1 1 2 0v1a1 1 0 1 1-2 0v-1zm6-4a1 1 0 1 1 2 0v5a1 1 0 1 1-2 0V7zM7 9a1 1 0 0 1 2 0v3a1 1 0 1 1-2 0V9z" />
                                <path
                                    d="M4 1.5H3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2V14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V3.5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1v1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1V14a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V3.5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1v-1z" />
                                <path
                                    d="M9.5 1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-3a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h3zm-3-1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 5 1.5v1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 6.5 4h3A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 11 2.5v-1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 9.5 0h-3z" />
                            </svg></div>

                        <h4>Complete peer evaluation</h4>
                        <p>Record the peer evaluation form for every group project</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>




                </div>

            </div>


        </div>



    </main>

    <p style="text-align: center; background-color: rgb(72, 196, 214); color: white; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
        Copyright © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> GroupMatesFinder. All Rights Reserved.</p>

</body>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: #f8f9f9ee;
    }

    .head {
        position: absolute;
        top: 5%;
        left: 4%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    .login {
        position: absolute;
        top: 5%;
        left: 95%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }


    .hero {
        /* Sizing */
        width: 98vw;
        height: 95vh;
        margin: auto;

        /* Flexbox stuff */
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;

        /* Text styles */
        text-align: center;
        color: black;
        background-color: #f8f9f9ee;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        /* Text styles */
        font-size: 5em;
        color: rgb(72, 196, 214);
        font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;

        /* Margins */
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;

    }

    .more-info-text {
        text-align: center;
        position: absolute;
        top: 87%;
        left: 46%;

        -webkit-animation: mover 2s infinite alternate;
        animation: mover 2s infinite alternate;

    }

    a {
        color: #39C0ED;
        text-decoration: none;
    }


    .btn {
        transition-duration: 0.4s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background-color: rgb(72, 196, 214);
        color: white;
    }

    /*  Text Animation - Learn More */

    @-webkit-keyframes mover {
        0% {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        100% {
            transform: translateY(-20px);
        }
    }

    @keyframes mover {
        0% {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        100% {
            transform: translateY(-20px);
        }
    }



    /* Big header - GroupMatesFinder */
    .ml6 {
        position: relative;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 3.3em;
        padding-top: 0.5em;
    }

    .ml6 .text-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
        padding-top: 0.4em;
        padding-right: 0.05em;
        overflow: hidden;

    }

    .ml6 .letter {
        display: inline-block;
        line-height: 1em;
        padding-bottom: 0.5em;
    }
</style>

<script>
    // Wrap every letter in a span
    var textWrapper = document.querySelector('.ml6 .letters');
    textWrapper.innerHTML = textWrapper.textContent.replace(/\S/g, "<span class='letter'>$&</span>");

    anime.timeline({ loop: false })
        .add({
            targets: '.ml6 .letter',
            translateY: ["1.6em", 0],
            translateZ: 0,
            duration: 750,
            delay: (el, i) => 50 * i
        });

</script>